Package edu.cnm.deepdive.jata.model.entity

Class UserGame

java.lang.Object
edu.cnm.deepdive.jata.model.entity.UserGame
@Entity public class UserGame extends Object
This class is the association of a user and a specific game. As ship locations and shots are specific to a user, the associate to each is included in this entity
